售售后服务方面的能力，树立良好的品牌形象。 中国有望成全球最大汽车出口国 商务部：三措施护航中国汽车出海"},"attached_info":"Cj8It9CBoZWsyKYeEAMaCDk2MjcxMjgyILexvKMGMA04rAFAJ3IJNjAyOTU5MTk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"42 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-52bb8cb88f53ddd29db1fac8a569cf9e_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1685056451.1330695","card_id":"Q_602999862","target":{"id":602999862,"title":"2023 年有哪些能让办公效率翻倍的数码好物推荐？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/602999862","type":"question","created":1685011333,"answer_count":318,"follower_count":346,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2566,7641,2632455,2645320,2710353],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8It9CBoZWsyKYeEAMaCDk2MjgwMjk2IIX3vKMGMAA42gJAKHIJNjAyOTk5ODYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"42 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b33772017e1ca13215869b232ab035f0_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"41_1685056451.1334956","card_id":"Q_602999825","target":{"id":602999825,"title":"2023 年你的背包中都有哪些数码产品，可以看下你的 EDC 吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/602999825","type":"question","created":1685011306,"answer_count":301,"follower_count":329,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[7641,221195,2632455,2645320,2710353],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8It9CBoZWsyKYeEAMaCDk2MjgwMjg3IOr2vKMGMAA4yQJAKXIJNjAyOTk5ODI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"42 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba9a8b454ec06b7577e1c6e98810ed76_b.jpg"}]},{"type